</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6E69E1FC46EFCADE816E003DB396AB48" pageId="780" pageNumber="781">
<taxonomicName id="CAF36FB834703F50388CBA3DED6F7D21" authorityName="LeConte" authorityYear="1853" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Trechicus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="780" pageNumber="781" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="umbripennis">Trechicus umbripennis</taxonomicName>
LeConte, 1853c: 386. Type locality: &quot;Georgia; Carolina&quot; (original citation). Three syntypes in MCZ [# 5791]. Synonymy established by Horn (1875: 126), confirmed by Bousquet (1987a: 128).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="AEAF74E862F7C1CDF307705C028C19C4" pageId="780" pageNumber="781">
